第71届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单于1999年2月9日由学院主席罗伯特·莱姆（{{lang|en|Robert Rehme}}）和[[男演员|男演员]][[凯文·斯派西|凯文·斯派西]]一起在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布<ref>{{cite news |last=Munoz |first=Lorena |title=It's the Early Birds That Get to Squirm |url=http://articles.latimes.com/1999/feb/10/entertainment/ca-6553 |accessdate=2014-02-27 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=1999-02-10 |archivedate=2014-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104100303/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/feb/10/entertainment/ca-6553 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《恋爱中的莎士比亚》以13项提名领跑，《拯救大兵瑞恩》则以11项紧随其后<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202124337/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1999-02-10/lifestyle/9902090688_1_71st-academy-awards-spielberg-private-ryan |last=Anthony |first=Todd |title=71st Academy Awards |archivedate=2014-02-02 |url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1999-02-10/lifestyle/9902090688_1_71st-academy-awards-spielberg-private-ryan |accessdate=2014-02-27 |work=Sun-Sentinel |publisher=Tribune Company |date=1999-02-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

获奖名单在1999年3月21日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news|title=Nominees & Winners for the 71st Academy Awards |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/1990-1999/71nominees.html |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102161927/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/1990-1999/71nominees.html |archivedate=2013-11-02 |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |publisher=AMPAS |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《美丽人生》是历史上第二部在同一年获得最佳影片和[[奥斯卡最佳外语片奖|外语片]]两项提名的电影<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|401}}，并且其七项提名也创下了非英语电影提名数量的新纪录<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|209}}。[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角奖]]得主[[罗伯托·贝尼尼|罗伯托·贝尼尼]]成为历史上第二位自导自演获奖的演员，第一位则是[[劳伦斯·奥利维尔|劳伦斯·奥利维尔]]因1948年的《[[哈姆雷特_(1948年电影)|哈姆雷特]]》获奖<ref>{{cite book | last = Osborne | first = Robert | title = 85 Years of the Oscar: The Complete History of the Academy Awards | year = 2013 | isbn = 0-7892-1142-4 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Abbeville Publishing Group | page = 423}}</ref>。贝尼尼还成为第四位因同一部电影获得表演、导演、编剧提名的电影人<ref>{{cite news | last = Welkos |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108041903/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/19/entertainment/ca-18710 |archivedate=2014-01-08 |deadurl=no |first=Robert W. |title=Benigni Rising Has Hollywood Gushing |url= http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/19/entertainment/ca-18710 |accessdate=2014-02-27 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=1999-03-19}}</ref>，并且是第三位凭一个没有说[[英语|英语]]的角色获奖的演员<ref>{{cite news |last=O'Neil |first=Tom |title=Quiz: Who won Oscars for foreign-lingo roles? |archivedate=2014-01-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116134359/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2010/09/oscars-academy-awards-825916374-entertainment-news.html |url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2010/09/oscars-academy-awards-825916374-entertainment-news.html |accessdate=2014-02-27 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2010-09-22}}</ref>。此外，[[凯特·布兰切特|凯特·布兰切特]]和[[朱迪·丹奇|朱迪·丹奇]]分别因扮演英国女王[[伊丽莎白一世_(英格兰)|伊丽莎白一世]]获得[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|女主角]]和[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角奖]]提名，这也成为历史上首次有两位女演员于同一年中分别在不同电影扮演同一角色而双双获得表演奖提名<ref>{{citation | last = Kinn | first = Gail | last2 = Piazza | first2 = Jim | title = The Academy Awards: The Complete Unofficial History | year = 2002 | isbn = 978-1579123963 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Workman Publishing Company | page = 299}}</ref>。

