== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Whoopi_Goldberg_at_a_NYC_No_on_Proposition_8_Rally.jpg|130px]]担任第71届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的主持人。]]

[[第70届奥斯卡金像奖|第70届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]在收视率上创下新高，并赢得了多项[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]，美国电影艺术与科学学院于是试图对晚会做出调整，以求保持这样的成绩，1998年6月，学院主持罗伯特·莱姆宣布颁奖典礼将于史上首度在[[星期日|星期日]]举行<ref>{{cite news |last=Madigan |first=Nick |title=Sunday officially Oscar's |archivedate=2014-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110222613/http://variety.com/1998/film/news/sunday-officially-oscar-s-1117477950/ |url=http://variety.com/1998/film/news/sunday-officially-oscar-s-1117477950/ |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Variety |publisher=PMC |date=1998-06-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。学院与[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]都希望将晚会定在这个日期能够有利于获得较高的收视率<ref>{{cite news |last=Welkos |first=Robert W. |title=Cinema's Super Sunday |archivedate=2014-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110224511/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/13/entertainment/ca-16738 |url=http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/13/entertainment/ca-16738 |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Los Angeles Times |deadurl=no |publisher=Tribune Company |date=1999-03-13}}</ref>。学院还表示，将典礼改在周日举行将令交通堵塞的问题得到缓解，因为周末时的交通量要远小于工作日<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|213}}。

1999年1月，吉尔·凯茨获选担任晚会电视直播的制片人<ref>{{cite news |last=Madigan |first=Nick |title=Cates to produce Oscars |url=http://variety.com/1999/film/news/cates-to-produce-oscars-1117489884/ |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Variety |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110233415/http://variety.com/1999/film/news/cates-to-produce-oscars-1117489884/ |archivedate=2014-01-10 |deadurl=no |publisher=PMC |date=1999-01-04}}</ref>，他立即就选择了奥斯卡金像奖得主，女演员乌比·戈德堡担任主持人<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|214}}。凯茨表示，自己选择戈德堡再次担任主持人是因为观众对她有一种崇拜和情感，并且她在节目主持上也有着过人的天赋<ref name="CNN">{{cite news |title=Whoopi! Goldberg to host Oscars |archivedate=2011-02-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110201022227/http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/News/9901/13/showbuzz/#story1 |url=http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/News/9901/13/showbuzz/#story1 |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=CNN |publisher=Time Warner |date=1999-01-13}}</ref>。戈德堡也在声明中表示自己对获选主持奥斯卡颁奖典礼深感荣幸：“我对能够陪同奥斯卡进入新千年感到非常高兴。谁能想到我会来主持本世纪的最后一场奥斯卡电视直播呢？这可是件大事。”<ref name="CNN" />

另外还有多人参与了颁奖典礼的制作。[[比尔·康堤|比尔·康堤]]（{{lang|en|Bill Conti}}）担任晚会的音乐总监<ref>{{cite news | title = Morning Report: Arts And Entertainment Reports From The Times, News Services And The Nations's Press |archivedate=2014-01-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110093511/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/jan/23/entertainment/ca-739/2 |url=http://articles.latimes.com/1999/jan/23/entertainment/ca-739/2 |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=1999-01-23}}</ref>。编舞[[黛比·艾伦|黛比·艾伦]]除了监督原创歌曲奖提名作品表演外还为正剧类原创配乐奖提名作品选段设计了一段舞蹈曲目，由来自世界各地的5位舞蹈家共同表演<ref name="Pond">{{citation |last=Pond |first=Steve |title=The Big Show: High Times and Dirty Dealings Backstage at the Academy Awards |year=2005 |isbn=0-571-21193-3 |location=New York, United States |edition= |OCLC=  |publisher=Faber and Faber}}</ref>{{rp|199}}。学院还首次专门制作了独家的红地毯节目在晚会开始前播出，这段全长半小时的节目由丹尼斯·多蒂（{{lang|en|Dennis Doty}}）监制，女演员[[吉娜·戴维斯|吉娜·戴维斯]]和{{lang|en|[[CNN|CNN]]}}记者吉姆·莫雷特共同主持<ref>{{cite news |last=Shister |first=Gail |title=CNN's Jim Moret Working Swing Shift On Oscar Night |archivedate=2014-01-10 |deadurl=no |date=1999-03-18 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140110224619/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1999-03-18/features/9903180292_1_jim-moret-showbiz-today-oscar-preview-show |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Chicago Tribune |publisher=Tribune Company |url= http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1999-03-18/features/9903180292_1_jim-moret-showbiz-today-oscar-preview-show}}</ref>。这场红地毯秀与其他电视台的内容类似，也包含对获提名艺人及其他嘉宾的采访，提名作品的概括，以及有关电视转播的幕后信息<ref name="Pond" />{{rp|211}}。

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
截止2月9日提名名单公布时，五部获最佳影片提名电影在[[美国电影|美国]]的总计[[票房|票房]]收入为3亿零198万4040美元，平均每部6039万6808美元<ref name="BoxOfficeMojoOscars">{{cite news |title=1998 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1998&p=.htm |accessdate=2014-02-28 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140221150403/http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1998&p=.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=Amazon.com |archivedate=2014-02-21 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。其中《拯救大兵瑞恩》以1亿9492万8728美元名列榜首，之后分别是收入3654万9292美元的《恋爱中的莎士比亚》，进账3062万4528美元的《细细的红线》，收入2139万4848美元的《伊丽莎白》和进账1848万6644美元的《美丽人生》<ref name="BoxOfficeMojoOscars" />。

在1998年美国电影票房50强中，有13部电影获得了共计36项提名。其中只有《拯救大兵瑞恩》（[[亚军|亚军]]）、《楚门的世界》（第11位）、《法网边缘》（第40位）和《原色）（第50位）这四部获得了最佳影片、导演、演员或编剧类奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars">{{cite web |archivedate=2014-01-10 |deadurl=no |work=Box Office Mojo |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140110155234/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=1999-02-08&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1998&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm |accessdate=2014-02-28 |publisher=Amazon.com |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=1999-02-08&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1998&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm |title=1998 Domestic Grosses}}</ref>。另外九部获提名的分别是《世界末日》（[[冠军|冠军]]）、《虫虫危机》（第5位）、《心灵点滴》（第12位）、《花木兰》（第13位）、《佐罗的面具》（第17位）、《埃及王子》（第18位）、《马语者》（第24位）、《美梦成真》（第37位）和《欢乐谷》（第49位）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
本场晚会所获得的媒体评价褒贬不一。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》专栏作家丽莎·施瓦兹包恩（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）打趣说“昨晚乌比震撼全场，她知道这一点——但是，她却把这种（震撼全场的）粗鲁变成了自己（可以）野蛮无理的象征”<ref>{{cite news|last=Schawrzbaum |first=Lisa |title=Vulgar disfavors |publisher=Time Warner |date=1999-03-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109225714/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C82753%2C00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-01-09 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,82753,00.html |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Entertainment Weekly }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》电视评论员汤姆·谢尔斯（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）哀叹戈德堡“花了大把时间来笑自己的笑话，这些笑话中很多都很下流，（或至少）有点下流。”他还毫不留情地批评了主持人对五部服装设计奖提名作品的呈现，称这既鸡肋，又浪费时间<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|244}}。《[[西雅图时报|西雅图时报]]》影评人约翰·哈特尔（{{lang|en|John Hartl}}）感叹称这“是本世纪最漫长，并且可以是最乏味的奥斯卡颁奖典礼，整整四个小时呐”<ref>{{cite news |last=Hartl |first=John |title=`Love' Conquers All{{ndash}}Oscar Gets Fickle In Night Of Close Calls And Upsets |url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19990322&slug=2950840 |accessdate=2014-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110090846/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19990322&slug=2950840 |archivedate=2014-01-10 |work=The Seattle Times |publisher=The Seattle Times Company |date=1999-03-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

其他媒体对晚会的评价更为正面。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》电视专栏作家罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）表示自己喜欢戈德堡主持中那种更清晰、更具社会意识的风格<ref>{{cite news |last=Bianco |first=Robert |title=Show makes lead of Hollywood gold |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Company |date=1999-03-22 |page=D1}}</ref>。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''Boston Globe''}}）电视评论员马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）称这是完美的一年，因为她可以有足够多的[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]式勾心斗角和争夺战来进行表演<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|244}}。《[[丹佛邮报|丹佛邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''Denver Post''}}）的乔安妮·奥斯特鲁夫（{{lang|en|Joanne Ostrow}}）断言乌比·戈德堡的表现比她之前两次主持更加出色，并认为“这场节目（进行得）异常顺利”<ref>{{cite news |last=Ostrow |first=Joanne |title=The African Queen trumps Billy Crystal |work=Denver Post |publisher=MediaNews Group |date=1999-03-22 |archivedate=2014-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110205302/http://extras.denverpost.com/scene/oscar0322c.htm |deadurl=no |url=http://extras.denverpost.com/scene/oscar0322c.htm |accessdate=2014-02-28}}</ref>。

=== 收视率和奖项 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有4551万观众收看，与[[第70届奥斯卡金像奖|去年]]相比降低了18%<ref name="Oscar ratings">{{cite news|last=Gorman |first=Bill |title=With No Blockbusters Up For Best Picture, Expect 'Academy Awards' Viewership To Fall; Ratings History + Your Guess For This Year (Poll) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210015818/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/24/with-no-blockbusters-up-for-best-picture-expect-academy-awards-viewership-to-fall-ratings-history-your-guess-for-this-year-poll/120239/ |archivedate=2013-12-10 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=''TV by the Numbers'' |publisher=Tribune Company |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/24/with-no-blockbusters-up-for-best-picture-expect-academy-awards-viewership-to-fall-ratings-history-your-guess-for-this-year-poll/120239/ |date=2012-02-24 }}</ref><ref name="LA Times Oscar Ratings">{{cite news |last=Lowry |first=Brian |title=Oscars Draw Big Numbers, Though Not as Big as Hoped |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140110093449/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/23/entertainment/ca-20046 |deadurl=no |url=http://articles.latimes.com/1999/mar/23/entertainment/ca-20046 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2014-02-28 |date=1999-03-23 |archivedate=2014-01-10}}</ref>，而所有曾观看部分播出时段节目的观众总数则估计有7810万<ref name="LA Times Oscar Ratings" />。从尼尔森收视率调查的数量看，节目的表现也不及去年，吸引了28.63%的[[家庭|家庭]]观看<ref>{{cite news |last=Bierbaum |first=Tom |title=Oscars don’t push aud envelope |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140110233148/http://variety.com/1999/tv/news/oscars-don-t-push-aud-envelope-1117492582/ |url=http://variety.com/1999/tv/news/oscars-don-t-push-aud-envelope-1117492582/ |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Variety |archivedate=2014-01-10 |deadurl=no |publisher=PMC |date=1999-03-22}}</ref>，在18至49岁年龄段观众群的收视率为18.8%<ref name="TVB Oscars">{{cite news|title=Academy Awards ratings |work=''Television Bureau of Advertising'' |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |archivedate=2013-09-27 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf |accessdate=2014-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927155318/http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf }}</ref>。

1999年7月，颁奖典礼获得了第51届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的7项提名<ref>{{cite news |title=Primetime Emmy database |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109223435/http://www.emmys.com/shows/71st-annual-academy-awards |url= http://www.emmys.com/shows/71st-annual-academy-awards |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Academy of Television Arts and Sciences |publisher=ATAS |archivedate=2014-01-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，并在两个月后赢得了综艺或音乐节目类杰出艺术指导奖以及剧情、综艺、迷你剧集、电视电影或特别节目类杰出灯光指导两座奖项<ref>{{cite news | title = 51st Annual Emmy Awards: Creative Arts Emmy Winners | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1999/sep/13/entertainment/ca-9838 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140110091506/http://articles.latimes.com/1999/sep/13/entertainment/ca-9838 | deadurl = no |accessdate=2014-02-28 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=1999-09-13 |archivedate=2014-01-10}}</ref>。

